ly replicated\", verifyFullyReplicated(lh, 3 * numEntries));\n+        lh.close();\n+    }\n+\n     /**\n      * This tests the asynchronous bookie recovery functionality by writing\n      * entries into 3 bookies, killing one bookie, starting up a new one to"}]}

